{"tid":2293096,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍國防升級！神盾艦首次在大氣層外攔截洲際飛彈","createTime":"2020-11-20T04:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T06:57:30.000Z","uid":105798,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f55b79290d7e67484954e334469d2de86d3d544f","tid":2293096,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"美國飛彈防禦署（Missile Defense Agency）宣布，16日在夏威夷東北部進行神盾驅逐艦的飛彈防禦系統攔截試驗，首次成功攔截一枚模擬的洲際彈道飛彈。<br />\n<br />\n據官方聲明，美軍先從太平洋馬紹爾群島（Marshall Islands）的瓜加林環礁（Kwajalein Atoll）試驗場發射洲際彈道飛彈，再由部署在夏威夷附近、配備神盾系統的伯克級驅逐艦「約翰芬恩號」（John Finn）發射「標準三型」（SM-3 Block II A）攔截飛彈，成功在地球大氣層外擊落目標。<br />\n<br />\n 過去的攔截測試都是在阿拉斯加或加州等陸地上進行，這項試射證實美軍在海上也具有攔截洲際彈道飛彈的能力，能夠抵禦來自北韓等國的威脅，代表美國將來可建構多層的「國土防護網」。飛彈防禦局長希爾（Jon Hill）強調這是「關鍵的里程碑，一項了不起的成就」。<br />\n<br />\n標準三型飛彈的Block II A型是由美國雷神公司和日本三菱重工共同研發，全長6.55公尺，飛行速度達到秒速4.5公里，最大射程1200公里、射高900至1050公里，不光是洲際飛彈，就連低軌道衛星也能擊落。"},{"pid":"ad45a7a90bd494caaec3efbdfa3919110c7cd118","tid":2293096,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"我國d東風點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8beb5f011f7c2292983aa1284a499d07b114c759","tid":2293096,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidaxe/2020/11/18/a-us-navy-destroyer-just-shot-down-an-icbm-target-expect-trouble-in-moscow-and-beijing/?sh=4ef398406a66\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fdavidaxe%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2Fa-us-navy-destroyer-just-shot-down-an-icbm-target-expect-trouble-in-moscow-and-beijing%2F%3Fsh%3D4ef398406a66&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BXf7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=5efd37b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidaxe/2020/11/18/a-us-navy-destroyer-just-shot-down-an-icbm-target-expect-trouble-in-moscow-and-beijing/?sh=4ef398406a66</a><br />\n<br />\nIn other words, it wasn&rsquo;t really an ICBM. A real ICBM probably would be much harder to shoot down.<br />\n<br />\nBut even this partially realistic test could have serious consequences. The world&rsquo;s nuclear powers for decades have deterred each other by maintaining <span class=\"red\">the mutual ability to destroy cities and military sites with atomic weapons.</span><br />\n<br />\nOnce one country can stop nuclear-tipped ICBMs, that mutual deterrence breaks down. The likely result is a fast-escalating arms race as newly vulnerable countries scramble to overcome each other&rsquo;s atomic defenses."},{"pid":"30e5ab748577dcead21680c76808fe86a0d99e3e","tid":2293096,"uid":49532,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ad45a7a90bd494caaec3efbdfa3919110c7cd118","tid":2293096,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"我國d東風點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"中風導彈"},{"pid":"1c5bb67f99204d5ac2ae2062e7e7a91dc2e16a00","tid":2293096,"uid":4857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不光是洲際飛彈，就連<span class=\"red\">低軌道衛星</span>也能擊落。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWIKI: 絕大多數對地觀測衛星、測地衛星、太空站以及一些新的通信衛星系統都採用低軌道。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade0c3e5a8868e29790973faa99ad1ff3bdc9ef0","tid":2293096,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c5bb67f99204d5ac2ae2062e7e7a91dc2e16a00","tid":2293096,"uid":4857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不光是洲際飛彈，就連<span class=\"red\">低軌道衛星</span>也能擊落。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWIKI: 絕大多數對地觀測衛星、測地衛星、太空站以及一些新的通信衛星系統都採用低軌道。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c